comment: This is the minimum ripple factor for a third-order Chebyshev filter for which the generalized reflectionless topology needs no negative elements. - _Matthew A. Morgan_, Oct 18 2017
link: Ivan Panchenko, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..1000
formula: Equals Sum_{k>=0} binomial(2*k,k) * k/16^k. - _Amiram Eldar_, Aug 02 2020
